      • wrapper

        public static Function<EventDAO,ItemEventDAO> wrapper()

        A function that wraps an event DAO in a prefetching item event DAO. If the DAO already implements ItemEventDAO, it is returned unwrapped.

        Returns:
        A wrapper function to make item event DAOs from event DAOs.
